    Process raw data

    process_text.Rd

    Process raw data

    Usage

    process_text(raw_data)

    Arguments

    raw_data

    Value

    tibble with standardized names, lowercase text, all character!

    Examples

    require(palmerpenguins)
#> Loading required package: palmerpenguins
process_text(palmerpenguins::penguins_raw)
